  <p>If you're a three-day tourist, the €30 membership fee costs you roughly €1–€2 per gram across your visit if you buy 15–20g. That's noise compared to the legal protection and guaranteed quality you're getting.</p>

  <p><strong>Also worth noting:</strong> Many tourist scams in Madrid involve "cannabis dealers" who take your money and disappear, or sell you fake product, or sell you cannabis then rob you afterward. Cannabis clubs eliminate this risk entirely.</p>

